data.value:
The Master Module is a Component Management System (CMS) designed for efficiently managing electronic components within an organization. It is built using VB.NET with an SQL Server database and is operated solely by an Admin.
* Project Description The system enables the Admin to manage the borrowing and returning of electronic components, track inventory, and handle user access. It provides a structured way to store and retrieve component details, ensuring an organized and efficient workflow.
* Key Features * Component Management:
Add, update, and delete electronic components in the additem table.
Store images of components via file paths in the database.
* Borrowing & Return Management:
Track borrowed items and their return status in the useritem table.
Update return status using radio buttons and a date-time picker.
* Database Integration:
SQL Server stores all component and borrowing records.
DataGridView is used for displaying and managing records.
